Package heif

Provides high-level classes for parsing and manipulating HEIF-based files.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BoxFactory  
    BoxHandler
    Handles parsing of HEIF/HEIC file structures based on the ISO Base Media Format.
    HeifParser
    Parses HEIF/HEIC image files and extracts embedded metadata.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HeifBoxType
    Defines all supported HEIF (High Efficiency Image File) box types.
    HeifBoxType.BoxCategory
    Describes the general role of the box in the file structure.

Package heif Description

Provides high-level classes for parsing and manipulating HEIF-based files.

This package includes core classes for handling HEIC, HEIF, and related ISO Base Media formats.

July 2025
